Janice Kawaye https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Janice_Kawaye 0 Janice Kawaye is an Japanese-American voice actress known for her roles as Ami in the cartoon Hi Hi Puffy AmiYumi which aired on Cartoon Network in the mid-2000s, Jenny, the title character in My Life as a Teenage Robot and Gi in Captain Planet and the Planeteers. In video games, she voices Ayane in the Ninja Gaiden series as well as Peko Pekoyama in the Danganronpa franchise.
